    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:1.1",
          "pli": "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:1.2",
          "pli": "Tena kho pana samayena sāvatthiyaṃ aññataro bhikkhu ahinā daṭṭho kālaṅkato hoti. ",
          "en": "Now, at that time a monk in Sāvatthī passed away due to a snake bite. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:1.3",
          "pli": "Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ: ",
          "en": "Then several mendicants went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:1.4",
          "pli": "“idha, bhante, sāvatthiyaṃ aññataro bhikkhu ahinā daṭṭho kālaṅkato”ti. ",
          "en": "“Sir, a monk in Sāvatthī has passed away due to a snake bite.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:2.1",
          "pli": "“Na hi nūna so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena phari. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, that monk mustn’t have spread a mind of love to the four royal snake families. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:2.2",
          "pli": "Sace hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena phareyya, na hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ahinā daṭṭho kālaṃ kareyya. ",
          "en": "If he had, he wouldn’t have died due to a snake bite. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:3.1",
          "pli": "Katamāni cattāri? ",
          "en": "What four? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:3.2",
          "pli": "Virūpakkhaṃ ahirājakulaṃ, erāpathaṃ ahirājakulaṃ, chabyāputtaṃ ahirājakulaṃ, kaṇhāgotamakaṃ ahirājakulaṃ. ",
          "en": "The royal snake families of Virūpakkha, Erāpatha, Chabyāputta, and Kaṇhāgotamaka. … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:3.3",
          "pli": "Na hi nūna so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu imāni cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena phari. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:3.4",
          "pli": "Sace hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu imāni cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena phareyya, na hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ahinā daṭṭho kālaṃ kareyya. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:4.1",
          "pli": "Anujānāmi, bhikkhave, imāni cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena pharituṃ attaguttiyā attarakkhāya attaparittāyāti. ",
          "en": "Mendicants, I urge you to spread a mind of love to the four royal snake families, for your own safety, security, and protection. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:5.1",
          "pli": "Virūpakkhehi me mettaṃ, ",
          "en": "I love the Virūpakkhas, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:5.2",
          "pli": "Mettaṃ erāpathehi me; ",
          "en": "the Erāpathas I love, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:5.3",
          "pli": "Chabyāputtehi me mettaṃ, ",
          "en": "I love the Chabyāputtas, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:5.4",
          "pli": "Mettaṃ kaṇhāgotamakehi ca. ",
          "en": "the Kaṇhāgotamakas I love. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:6.1",
          "pli": "Apādakehi me mettaṃ, ",
          "en": "I love the footless creatures, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:6.2",
          "pli": "mettaṃ dvipādakehi me; ",
          "en": "the two-footed I love, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:6.3",
          "pli": "Catuppadehi me mettaṃ, ",
          "en": "I love the four-footed, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:6.4",
          "pli": "mettaṃ bahuppadehi me. ",
          "en": "the many-footed I love. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:7.1",
          "pli": "Mā maṃ apādako hiṃsi, ",
          "en": "May the footless not harm me! "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:7.2",
          "pli": "mā maṃ hiṃsi dvipādako; ",
          "en": "May I not be harmed by the two-footed! "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:7.3",
          "pli": "Mā maṃ catuppado hiṃsi, ",
          "en": "May the four-footed not harm me! "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:7.4",
          "pli": "mā maṃ hiṃsi bahuppado. ",
          "en": "May I not be harmed by the many-footed! "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:8.1",
          "pli": "Sabbe sattā sabbe pāṇā, ",
          "en": "All sentient beings, all living things, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:8.2",
          "pli": "sabbe bhūtā ca kevalā; ",
          "en": "all creatures, every one: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:8.3",
          "pli": "Sabbe bhadrāni passantu, ",
          "en": "may they see only nice things, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:8.4",
          "pli": "mā kañci pāpamāgamā. ",
          "en": "may bad not come to anyone. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:9.1",
          "pli": "Appamāṇo buddho, ",
          "en": "The Buddha is immeasurable, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:9.2",
          "pli": "Appamāṇo dhammo; ",
          "en": "the teaching is immeasurable, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:9.3",
          "pli": "Appamāṇo saṃgho, ",
          "en": "the Saṅgha is immeasurable. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:9.4",
          "pli": "Pamāṇavantāni sarīsapāni. ",
          "en": "But limited are crawling things, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:10.1",
          "pli": "Ahivicchikā satapadī, ",
          "en": "snakes and scorpions, centipedes, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:10.2",
          "pli": "Uṇṇanābhī sarabū mūsikā; ",
          "en": "spiders and lizards and mice. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:10.3",
          "pli": "Katā me rakkhā katā me parittā, ",
          "en": "I’ve made this safeguard, I’ve made this protection: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:10.4",
          "pli": "Paṭikkamantu bhūtāni; ",
          "en": "go away, creatures! "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:10.5",
          "pli": "Sohaṃ namo bhagavato, ",
          "en": "And so I revere the Blessed One, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:10.6",
          "pli": "Namo sattannaṃ sammāsambuddhānan”ti. ",
          "en": "I revere the seven perfectly awakened Buddhas.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.67:10.7",
          "pli": "Sattamaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
